<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="I" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Impale" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Impale,</orth> to encircle, to surround: <cit><quote>round --d with a glorious crown,</quote> <bibl n="shak. 3h6 3.2.171" default="NO" valid="yes">H6C III, 2, 171</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>did I i. him with the regal crown,</quote> <bibl n="shak. 3h6 3.3.189" default="NO" valid="yes">III, 3, 189</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>i. him with your weapons round about,</quote> <bibl n="shak. tro 5.7.5" default="NO" valid="yes">Troil. V, 7, 5</bibl></cit>.
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>